dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Sauk County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data group represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Sauk_Roads_2020' and 'Sauk_ROW_2020'. [Roads: This feature class contains detailed line work supporting Sauk Counties road network and contains street name, classification, and address range attributes.ROW: The primary division of a simultaneous conveyance and generally referred to as lots, units, or common elements.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most recent data for this county, please visit: http://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com.
